Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人君 想帶走她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靠你的劍 用你的二刀流來奪走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果贏了我 就可以帶走亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 若是你敗給了我 就得加入血盟騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 如果你那麼希望劍下見真章
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就以對決來分出高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:28.38,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\blur3\pos(544,506)}2024年10月20日      第75層 科力尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好位子所剩無幾了 要買就趁早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}活著的傳說 希茲克利夫 VS  二刀流的惡魔 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！你這笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要答應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好 都是我不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一時受不了挑釁就脫口而出了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…之前看見桐人你的二刀流時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的覺得像是另一個次元的強度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過團長他的特有技能也是一樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我也數次親眼見識到過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光芒自在的劍技 神聖劍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且不說攻擊 其防禦力都是壓倒性的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來就沒看到過 團長的HP條減少到黃色區域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的無敵 可以說已經超越了遊戲的平衡度了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 如果輸了 我不能休假也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連桐人你都得加入血盟騎士團才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 我也不會那麼簡單就輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:39.86,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めてた　臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:39.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去認同它  那懦弱的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:46.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わからないままに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:46.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使現在還不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:49.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怖がっていた　後ろの自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:49.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經懼怕的 身後的另一個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:56.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現実を 今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:56.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時卻將現實 呈現於此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:02:02.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:02:02.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾描繪過的無數的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:06.72,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここはきっと　儚い心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:06.72,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏有著 能將我這脆弱的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:09.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:09.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擾亂的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:13.78,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢で 高く跳んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:13.78,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓夢想去高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:20.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体どんな不安纏っても振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:20.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將身懷的所有不安 都統統拋去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:24.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠る　小さな思い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:24.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要放飛這份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:26.77,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拡がり出して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:26.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深藏心中地小小的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付く　弱い　私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你注意到這弱小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:32.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がいれば　暗い世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:32.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只要有你在  就算在深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:35.93,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:35.93,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能無所畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:41.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長い夢見る心は　そう　永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:41.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願次長夢的心  永存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:45.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:45.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:50.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I give you every thing I have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:50.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I give you every thing I have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\c&HE1BE56&\3c&H080808&\bord1\pos(517,458)\be2}紅色的殺意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉啊桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不知道事情會變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要收取演出費的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 比賽之後你就是我們公會的團員了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把這次的對決當作是隊務之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}你要接受決鬥的申請嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用盾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起的反應速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的防禦才真是完美的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以 還可以再快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\be3\blur3\an8\fs26}本片字幕由異域字幕組(www.yydm.com)製作,僅供試看之用,如果喜歡本作品,請購買並支持正版!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\be3\blur3\an8\fs26}翻譯 童話 明撒 永叔 天井 步 校譯 茶 時間 鹿 後期 小克 壓制 追憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什……麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.68,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)\be2\blur3\pos(541,501)}2024年10月22日      第五十層 阿爾格特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不是拜託他們拿件樸素點的來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件已經很樸素了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是我連累你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這也是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨行攻略也快到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能這麼說我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要避開公會… 遠離人群…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定不只是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身為封測者和獨特技能使用者的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為桐人你真的很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是很久以前的事了……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是一年多以前吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一度加入過一個公會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算上我也就只有六個人的小公會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫做月夜的黑貓團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白說 他們的等級比我低太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在被他們邀請時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說出自己的等級的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們肯定不會要我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我隱瞞了自己真正的等級 加入了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常羨慕他們那種如同在家一般的融洽氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是某一天……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的緣故 公會團滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有隱瞞我是封測者的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 應該就能讓他們知道陷阱的危險性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我害死了大家…和小幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我……會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:14.73,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)\be2\blur3\pos(526,504)}2024年10月23日     第55層 格朗薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訓練？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組成包括我在內的三人小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破第五十五層的迷宮區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 哥德夫利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人就由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說你是副團長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但無視紀律的話 也會讓人很難辦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且既然他加入了公會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我這個擔當先鋒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來鑒定下他的實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑…憑桐人的實力 才不會給你添麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼三十分鐘後 在城鎮的西門集合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得兩個人組隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏等著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這裏這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起 大家都是一個公會的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想借此機會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把之前的恩怨都一筆勾銷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天 給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會再對你無禮了 請原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣就了結了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 今天的訓練是鑒定處理危機時的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位的水晶道具請交由我保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移水晶也要？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼大家出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:21.96,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\blur3\pos(517,502)}第55層·迷宮區前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 就在這裏休息一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 分發給你們食物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中麻痹了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備這個水的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉德爾 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把解毒結晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥德夫利先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你就是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真四肢發達頭腦簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的隊伍…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣被犯罪者玩家的大軍團襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇戰到底 最後兩人死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的擊退了犯罪者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 我就為了你這小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把不相干的人給殺了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但相反的 你倒是好像挺高興的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會加入了血盟騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪者公會明顯更適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真會說有趣的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有眼力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…殺人公會微笑棺材的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個麻痹技巧也是在那裏學的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 不好 談話不到這裏為止的話 毒就要解掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中毒狀態還沒有消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要死了是怎樣的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…就要這樣死掉麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！喂！快說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什……！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 怎麼 果然還是很怕死麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 還不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 不這樣可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 死吧 死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回復！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了 幸好趕上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 謝謝你讓我趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地圖上尋找桐人君的位置時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到哥德夫利的反應消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在想是不是出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著對吧 桐人君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等我一下 馬上就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜大人 這只是訓練…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 只是訓練時發生了一些意外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  是我錯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會離開公會 再也不出現在你們面前的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了 副團長大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個…殺人者…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 都是…都是我害得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我…再也沒有臉見桐人君了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命是屬於你的 亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以將為你而活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最後一刻我都會和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…我也一定會守護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後永遠的守護著你 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼事 我都會讓你回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到那個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…今晚 想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.69,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)\be2\blur3\pos(517,502)}第61層·瑟爾穆布魯格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐…桐人君也快點脫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我這樣 羞…羞死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚想和你呆在同一個房間裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅如此…而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨…笨…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像做了個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢到原來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夢裏一直想著如果艾因格朗特的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇見桐人的事都是夢的話該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想回去 但不想失去在這裏度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對我來說這也是非常重要的兩年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我也這樣堅信著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 桐人君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能稍稍離開前線一段時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上上戰場的話 好像又會發生不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是有些累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22層的西南區域裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個被森林和湖水環繞的小村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個搬去那裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:29.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠くに聞こえた　鐘の音が少し寂しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:29.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從遠處傳來的鐘聲 傳達著淡淡的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:34.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:34.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次地努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:41.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今度は高く　駆け抜けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:41.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定能達到更高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:47.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ繰り返す現実も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:47.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是在無限反覆著的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:53.68,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}星の数の願い事も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:53.68,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}還是那些如同繁星般多的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:58.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}目指すべき明日を見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:58.89,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}在找到前進方向的我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:04.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}この想いには勝てない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:04.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}全都戰勝不了這份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:11.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}目の前に開かれた果てない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:11.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}在眼前無限延伸的這沒有盡頭的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:15.21,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}たとえ仮想でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:15.21,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}即使是夢也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:18.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}迷い続けても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:18.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}就算會一直迷路下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:22.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}夢の奥で強く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:22.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}只要能在這夢中變強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:27.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}ずっと　ずっと　響いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:27.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}願此思念 永遠響徹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:34.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}そっと　そっと　光ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:34.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}願此思念 永遠閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(136,571)}下回 朝露的少女

